Hello&nbsp; 
  We are still testing the Multicarrier app. Since we do, we get Duty invoices from FEDEX but this should not be the case because all our clients pay duties themselves. Can you please double check if the settings are correct? We pay the shipping but all clients outside EU pay themselves for the duties and other costs. No exceptions.&nbsp;  
  Thanks a lot to check this because this can be very expensive for us.&nbsp;  
  Best  Filip

